To clarify here, both

import onnx

as well as

import torch

on their own work without problems. This looks to me as if there is a problem with the loaded native libs / shared libs when both onnx and torch gets imported.

body:
To clarify here, both

    import onnx

as well as

    import torch

on their own work without problems. This looks to me as if there is a problem with the loaded native libs / shared libs when both onnx and torch gets imported.
